  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non\u2011stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "Lightly toast the bread slices in the skillet for 1\u20132\u202fmin per side until golden.",
    "Spread \u00bd tablespoon of sugar\u2011free jam on each slice and let it caramelize slightly.",
    "Lay 1\u202foz of jam\u00f3n serrano over the jam, then top with Manchego cheese slices.",
    "Drizzle olive oil over the cheese and sprinkle sea salt, pepper, rosemary, and lemon zest.",
    "Cover the skillet with a lid and cook for 3\u20134\u202fmin until the cheese is fully melted and bubbly.",
    "Remove the toast from the skillet and transfer to a plate.",
    "Garnish with a handful of microgreens or arugula for a fresh crunch.",
    "Serve immediately while the cheese is still warm and gooey."
  ],
